        API Reference
      </div>
      <p>Complete API documentation for developers</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/docs/components" class="card">
      <div class="card-title">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="20"
          height="20"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
