      Version 2.0 Released
    </div>
    <p>
      We've released version 2.0 of Gradiant with many new features and
      improvements. Check out the <a href="/docs/changelog">changelog</a> for details.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-4">
      <span class="badge">New Feature</span>
      <span class="badge">Performance</span>
      <span class="badge">Security</span>
    </div>
  </div>

